# New Feature Checklist

Replace `foo_bar` / `FooBar` with your feature name throughout.

## 1. Create files

```
lib/features/foo_bar/
  data/
    models/        foo_bar_model.dart        ← @freezed + @JsonSerializable
    datasources/   foo_bar_data_source.dart  ← extends ApiClient
    repositories/  foo_bar_repository.dart   ← Either<Failure, T> returns
  view/
    pages/         foo_bar_page.dart         ← BlocProvider → injector<FooBarCubit>()
    widgets/       (sub-widgets as needed)
  viewModel/       foo_bar_cubit.dart        ← Cubit<DefaultState<FooBarModel>>
```

## 2. Add route

`lib/config/routes/app_routes.dart`:
```dart
static const String fooBar = 'foo_bar';
```

`lib/config/routes/app_router.dart`:
```dart
GoRoute(
  path: '/${AppRoutes.fooBar}',
  name: AppRoutes.fooBar,
  builder: (_, __) => const FooBarPage(),
),
```

## 3. Create DI module

`lib/core/di/modules/foo_bar_module.dart`:
```dart
class FooBarModule {
  static void register() {
    injector.registerLazySingleton(
      () => FooBarDataSource(dio: injector<Dio>()),
    );
    injector.registerLazySingleton(
      () => FooBarRepository(dataSource: injector<FooBarDataSource>()),
    );
    injector.registerFactory(
      () => FooBarCubit(repository: injector<FooBarRepository>()),
    );
  }
}
```

`lib/core/di/service_locator.dart` — add inside `injectDependencies()`:
```dart
FooBarModule.register();
```

## 4. Generate code

```bash
dart run build_runner build --delete-conflicting-outputs
```

## Checklist

- [ ] Model with `@freezed` + both `part` directives
- [ ] DataSource extending `ApiClient`, using `requestAPI()`
- [ ] Repository returning `Either<Failure, T>`, using `left` / `right()`
- [ ] Cubit emitting `loading` → `success` / `fail`
- [ ] Page providing cubit via `BlocProvider(create: (_) => injector<FooBarCubit>())`
- [ ] Route name added to `AppRoutes`, route added to `AppRouter`
- [ ] DI module created and registered in `ServiceLocator`
- [ ] Code generation run
